name: Pink Lemonade Invitation
description:
Pink Lemonade and Sunshine! A perfect invitation for the sweetest of little girls. This vintage beauty will be the stunner for your party. Pair it will the party pack for maximum sweetness! Can also be used for a baby shower.

Purchase the listing and send your customized info (name, date, etc) to designsbyhellolove@gmail.com.

A proof will be emailed to you within 24-48hrs M-F.

I can also print for you. These are printed on beautiful linen stock perfect for this vintage feels.

Choose 4x6 or 5x7 for $1 each with envelopes.

Thanks for looking and happy birthday!

name: Fairy Tale Birth Announcement
description:

This beautiful birth announcement with surely steal the hearts of everyone that is special enough to receive it. It's soft pinks and classic style is the only way to announce your new bundle of joy.

This is fully customizable. Please purchase the listing an send all customization (baby name, parents, weight, length, time) to designsbyhellolove@gmail.com. 

Your order will be emailed back to you within 24-48 M-F. You may print yourself or I can print for you.

Thanks for looking! And congrats on your new princess!
